---
title: Portabello Mushroom, Bacon & Veggie Lasagne with Bechamel Sauce & Parmesan
description: Lasagnes are a much-loved dinnertime staple and with a stack of shrooms’, veggies and a delightfully creamy
bechamel sauce it will become unbeatable. The sharp Parmesan topping brings an extra zap of flavour and you’ll
adore how the cheese pulls away in strings when you slice up and serve this gorgeous dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
